    <briefdescription>
<para>Modbus TCP ADU (MBAP) framing layer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements Modbus TCP MBAP (Modbus Application Protocol) header framing over TCP transport sockets (syn_transport_tcp).</para>
<para>MBAP Header Structure (7 bytes):<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Transaction ID (2 bytes, big-endian)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Protocol ID (2 bytes, big-endian, 0x0000 = Modbus)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Length (2 bytes, big-endian, length of remaining bytes)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Unit ID (1 byte, target slave/server address)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Followed by standard Modbus PDU (Function Code + Data). Note that Modbus TCP does NOT include RTU CRC-16. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
